data.description: Recent price improvement for a quick sale! This 2017 townhome has lots of upgrades and is ready for its new family. Inside you will find nice wood floors throughout the open floor plan main floor. The kitchen has beautiful ebony colored staggered cabinets with crown molding which pairs perfectly with the white granite countertops and the stainless steel appliances. A nice covered back porch and a storage closet is found just outside the dining room door. Upstairs you will find the laundry room, the nice sized master bedroom with ensuite, 2 more guest bedrooms and a full bath. Located just off hwy 52, you are less than 10 miles from for Navy weapons station, 5 miles from all 3 schools (elem, middle, high) and within 2 miles of shopping and restaurants.
